page.title: 07FORE STREET CONT'D
page.content: The rest of the street is lined with shops: 2 Supermarkets, 2 Chemists, a Jeweller, a Tobacco/Sweet Shop, a Men's Out- fitters, a Second-hand , a Furniture , a Hardware & Garden ,& a Fabric/Curtain , the South Western Electricity Board, a Gift Card, Fruit & Vegetables, a Butcher,a Woolworth's, an Optician, a Newsagent's, a Bakery, a Discount Store, W.H.Smith's (stationers), Millets (camping/leisure wear), Sports (Game/hunting), a shop for the Imperial Cancer Research, & a Betting Shop. Behind Woolworth's Store is Wellington Printers. Before Fore Street joins Mantle Street we have a carpark to the right and a new housing cul-de-sac to the left.
